            "heading": "Mid-Drive Motor",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>Smoothing riding is a piece of cake with ALPHA's powerful MIVICE mid-drive motor.  It optimizes the weight distribution for a stable and comfortable ride. The mid-drive motor, with 5 levels of pedal assistance, helps riders take full control over every journey.</p>",
