            "heading": "105 N·m Torque",
            "heading_size": "text-lg-2xl",
            "text": "<p>With 105 N·m of torque, ALPHA delivers powerful acceleration, effortless hill climbing, and superior off-road performance. This high torque ensures a smooth and responsive ride. You will find ALPHA perfect for easily tackling steep inclines and rough terrains.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "highlighted_text": "none",
            "highlighted_scribble": "circle"
